Jack Hulbert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Hulbert 0 John Norman "Jack" Hulbert (24 April 1892 – 25 March 1978) was a British actor, director, screenwriter and singer, specializing primarily in comedy productions, and often working alongside his wife Cicely Courtneidge.
